title: clear_selected_folders()
brief: Clear all selected folders.
seealso: add_selected_folder, toggle_selected_folder, selected_folders, set_selected_folder
----

<p><tt>lumail</tt> allows you to select multiple folders to open at the same time.</p>
<p>The <tt>clear_selected_folders()</tt> function allows you to unselect all currently selected folders.</p>
